00:18:09.970 --> 00:18:12.750
You know what, we did not think
about audio side of things.

00:18:12.750 --> 00:18:15.250
I'm going to turn this up, and
hopefully you can pick it up.

00:18:15.250 --> 00:18:18.970
And actually, what I'll do is
I'll set this down over here.

00:18:18.970 --> 00:18:22.960
So here's what we ended
up putting together.

00:18:22.960 --> 00:18:25.670
It was something that
was out of nowhere

00:18:25.670 --> 00:18:29.460
with virtually no
preparation, and I

00:18:29.460 --> 00:18:32.700
wanted to show respect
and make it not fun.

00:18:32.700 --> 00:18:35.730
So this is what we did.

00:18:35.730 --> 00:18:39.630
And I will click refresh,
and we will watch another ad.

00:18:42.920 --> 00:18:45.750
Oh, oh, oh oh!

00:18:45.750 --> 00:18:47.440
And let me back this up.

00:18:47.440 --> 00:18:50.312
I don't know if we
can-- do we have audio?

00:18:50.312 --> 00:18:51.020
Or you know what?

00:18:51.020 --> 00:18:51.890
I'll just lay this.

00:18:51.890 --> 00:18:53.130
How about that.

00:18:53.130 --> 00:18:54.755
There we go.

00:18:54.755 --> 00:18:56.150
Boom.

