ANDY: Well, thanks,
Brian, for coming out.

00:32:30.620 --> 00:32:32.571
We really appreciate it.

00:32:32.571 --> 00:32:34.320
Yeah, it was great
hearing from you today.

00:32:34.320 --> 00:32:34.920
BRIAN BUSHWOOD:
You got it, Andy.

00:32:34.920 --> 00:32:35.753
Thanks so much guys.

